Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Encounters are mysterious!\NBut the world is even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is finally Masked Yaiba!\NInside the costume is an incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Masked Yaiba Murder Case."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're eating out today, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm meeting them\Nin front of this shrine at 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so lucky. Is it eel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think a good curry\Nrestaurant opened up near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a jumbo fried shrimp curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Laser Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laser Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police squad in Masked Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi, kids. Are you fans of Masked Yaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Masked Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean they're\Nfilming Masked Yaiba at this shrine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This gun's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This gun is important for\Nfighting monsters, so only I can touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to eat curry with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! The more the merrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who's gonna pay for 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but call your moms first,\Nso they won't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of parents are they,\Nall saying, "That would be great!"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Masked Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First the Laser Police, and now\NMasked Yaiba? What's with today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Aren't you Mori Kogoro-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nthe great detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is incredible!\NI'm a big fan! Let me shake your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! He's shaking\Nhands with Masked Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not the real Masked Yaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:37.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutsumi Yasuyuki (21) Jonan University, Law Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsutsumi Yasuyuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm a member of a college fan club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! He isn't Masked Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the real one\Nlooks a lot more handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for disappointing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that other person was also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say! Want to come to a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fan club is having a costume party!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I won't have\Nto pay for their food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're invited too, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NThere'll be beer, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Beer?! I'd love to! I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you won't have to pay for your beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party is in the basement of this mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all the monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Monkeyshroom\Nand Pork-n-Bones are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mole Alien, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}. Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our club's president,\NSaotome Madoka-{\i1}san{\i0}. This is her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a college student?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm in my third year studying literature!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:47.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Saotome Madoka (21) Shirakaba Women's College
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor to speak with the great Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can recount my humble exploits\Nanytime you want, day or night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who\Nshe's dressed up as?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Natsume Rei, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct! You must tune in a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever watched\NMasked Yaiba, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really like to, but I'm so\Nbusy with work that time of day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like drinking that time of day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masked Yaiba is really a young\Nman who sells hot dogs at the park
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Natsume Rei,\Nhis childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time an incident occurs,\Nhe rushes there on his motorcycle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fights the\Nevil bad guys and aliens!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Natsume Rei doesn't\Nknow his secret identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's always ditching work\Nto rush off on his motorcycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, Natsume Rei\Nforgives him with gentle feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason,\NI somehow know how that feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that does\Nsound kind of like me and Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone! Let's go to\Nthe tables! We have some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about me, Madoka-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She loves kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wish I could be a kid again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be an adult again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Honda! You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sorry. It took longer than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:21.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda Osamu (21) Jonan Univ., Engineering Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's that other guy. I guess\Nhe is a member of the fan club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why're you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd change things up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shock. You've only ever\Ndressed as Masked Yaiba before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! This is Mori Kogoro-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nthe famous detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mori?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Honda Osamu. He's in his\Nthird year of engineering at Jonan U.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only been in the club half a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's a very\Npassionate Masked Yaiba fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:08:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gun wouldn't\Nhappen to be real, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly! It's only\Na model! See for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's well-made!\NHe's a real gun fanatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The texture and weight are impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bullets are all blanks.\NThe barrel is plugged too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}! Won't you\Ncome and tell us a story?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Madoka-{\i1}san{\i0}! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over to the tables, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:51.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishima Katsuji (21) Toto University, P.E. Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough! Get ready, Honda! I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishima-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Mishima! What did I ever do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Mishima! Let's talk it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bulletproof vest...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing this saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no burn mark on his temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, he kept the\Ngun away from his head when he shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deceased is\NMishima Katsuji-{\i1}san{\i0}, age 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A third year student at Toto U.'s\Nphysical education department.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a genuine suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we all witnessed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still... this is a rather odd sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Laser Police always wear\Nthese vests when fighting monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I bought one\Nfrom a security store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, convinced he'd killed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishima-{\i1}san {\i0}then\Nshot himself in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would he try to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun {\i0}and Mishima-{\i1}kun \N{\i0}were actually very good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About ten days ago,\Nwhen we had gathered to plan this party,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishima-{\i1}kun {\i0}got mad at an\Noff-hand comment by Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stormed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him, "Your motorcycle is lame."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd! Nobody would\Nbe driven to murder because of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not as crazy as it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was especially obsessive\Nabout Masked Yaiba, even among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He spent half a year\Nremodeling a normal motorcycle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into a Masked Yaiba motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:12:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can understand why making\Nfun of it would make him mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's the\Nonly way to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His explanation seems truthful enough.\NBut something bugs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something\Nabout this incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure.\NThe gun was a modified model gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bullet in the bulletproof\Nvest was also made by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Mishima-{\i1}san \N{\i0}knowledgeable about guns at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He once asked me the difference\Nbetween automatics and revolvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, do all\NMasked Yaiba members...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what characters\Nin Masked Yaiba carry guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the Laser Police carry guns, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masked Yaiba himself doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:13:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Masked Yaiba\Nhas no need for guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always fights with his bare hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that leaves\Ntoo many things unclear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is shocking to see\Nsomething like this happen, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure. I guess TV dramas\Naren't entirely fiction after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dramas? Acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the mysteries connect now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my theory is correct,\Nit solves all the mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... Committing\Na murder right in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof! I need to find undeniable proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! As I recall--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta! Let me borrow your\NDetective League badge for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0} did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... he asked me to get it examined\Nright away. Says it's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, I'd like to\Ntake Honda to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the bulletproof vest on,\Nhe was shot from close range.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He could have a cracked rib.\NLet's drive him there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? W-Why--?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait until later\Nto take him to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to solve the mystery\Nof this detestable murder for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about, Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Mishima-{\i1}san {\i0}commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... this was a bonafide murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plotted by a certain\Nsomeone from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This someone suggested to Mishima-{\i1}san{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they act out a little play\Nto surprise everyone at the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Act?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In it, Mishima-{\i1}san {\i0}would pretend\Nto shoot someone, then kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To lay the groundwork for this,\Nthey had a fake argument beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... that someone was you,\NHonda Osamu-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you modified two\Nmodel guns of the same type
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and prepared two types of bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One type was a real lead bullet.\NThe other was an empty "blank."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You initially gave Mishima-{\i1}san\N{\i0}the gun with the blanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, before the party began,\Nyou met him at the Beika Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and switched his gun\Nwith the gun with real bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably by saying\Nyou were doing final checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the gun on Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\Nhip is Mishima-{\i1}san{\i0}'s?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait. Wasn't the\Nbarrel of that gun plugged?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the gun with\Nreal bullets wasn't plugged...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't Mishima-{\i1}san {\i0}have noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... the gun he handed\NMishima-{\i1}san {\i0}wasn't plugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He plugged it after the switch,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he wouldn't\Nrouse suspicion after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san {\i0}dressed\Nup as a Laser Police member
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of his usual\Nchoice of Masked Yaiba
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it wouldn't seem\Nstrange for a Laser Police member
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to carry a gun and\Nwear a bulletproof vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Mishima-{\i1}san{\i0} jumped down,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you moved as if taking\Nus out of harm's way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was actually to make\Nyou an easier target for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't Mishima know something\Nwas up if a real bullet came out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and Honda-{\i1}san\N{\i0}had probably done rehearsals
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in which he would pretend to be\Nhit the same time the gun sounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, after seeing Honda-{\i1}san\N{\i0}being "hit" this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishima-{\i1}san {\i0}believed it was\Njust like it was during rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your so-called "autosuggestion."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you have any evidence\Nthat he didn't commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to kill yourself by\Nputting a gun to your head and firing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,burn marks would be left on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there were none on Mishima-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with blanks,\Nit still produces a small flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why he held the\Ngun slightly away from his head,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to prevent being burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be sure about that!\NHe was a weird guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then allow me to show you some proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Examiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another set of fingerprints not\Nbelonging to the late Mishima-{\i1}san{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was found on this gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They also match the\Nchild's fingerprints on this badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}! When did you\Ntouch Mishima-{\i1}san{\i0}'s gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Genta didn't touch Mishima-{\i1}san{\i0}'s gun,\Nhow did his prints get on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer to that is... Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ran into us at the Beika Shrine\Nbefore coming here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This gun's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He touched it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact you had Mishima-{\i1}san{\i0}'s gun then
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is evidence that\Nyou switched your guns later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}. When did\Nyou start to suspect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutsumi-{\i1}san {\i0}said that\Nyou were a real gun aficionado.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you had a plugged gun.\NThat seemed odd to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Plugging the gun to be\Nextra safe proved to be my downfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishima...\Nkilled my kid brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:20:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years ago, my brother Hiroshi\Nwas heading to a friend's house
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:02.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To Hiroshi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a Masked Yaiba signboard
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he won in a magazine contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi died two days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His final words were,\N"Get Masked Yaiba to catch him..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined a number of Masked Yaiba\Nfan clubs to gather information
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and figure out who stole it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, half a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mishima finally\Nshowed me that signboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said his older brother\Nhad won it and given it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't have\Na brother named Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then you got your revenge on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, it's not\Ndiscussed in the TV drama,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Masked Yaiba has a back\Nstory in which his sister was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined fan clubs to kill the person\Nwho drove my brother to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but at some point, I began\Nto feel just like Masked Yaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Masked Yaiba are nothing alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masked Yaiba doesn't fight for revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He fights for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the children are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame you were that\Nwrong about Masked Yaiba all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yoko-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s on\Na music show starting at 7:30!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.65,0:23:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but we're watching\NMasked Yaiba at 7:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We never watch that junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to watch it starting tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Masked Yaiba fights for justice!\NWe gotta support him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!\NWhat about Yoko-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's sings for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This old guy's gonna live a long life...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That was President Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this sticky stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.47,0:24:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was a completely locked room...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might not have been an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible it was a murder\Nplotted by one of these people!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.44,0:24:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Honey Cocktail Murder Case."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.21,0:24:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.52,0:24:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.75,0:24:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode's case tastes like honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.30,0:24:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweetie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.98,0:24:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.90,0:24:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you call me honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.68,0:24:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
